  <p>The work is funded by the work. E5 Enclave does not wait for permission or philanthropy. We compete for federal contracts, apply for government grants, and build institutional partnerships that resource the pillars directly. Every dollar is deployed against the structural conditions documented in the BDI Sovereign Dataset.</p>
</div>

